{"tid":1887430,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得喺屋企讀書仲高質過返學","createTime":"2020-02-19T13:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T05:08:10.000Z","uid":134997,"like":26,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1f5d3cd403dd955270b6a73e7a15e4a082a8525e","tid":1887430,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T13:58:51.000Z","msg":"真 係 好 鍾 意 ZOOM<br />\n平時教得好嘅professor 成日唔得閒，依家有zoom 就可以開多好多高質extra tutorials<br />\n唔洗自己R tutorial R 得咁辛苦，又唔洗爭clinic 位，老師又唔洗約咁多group 學生教咁多次<br />\n今日上啲lectures 全部都 好 高 質，聽得好爽<br />\n雖然有時有人冇mute mic，但收音一定好過我用自己耳仔現場聽，比現實清楚好多<br />\nChatroom 有private message 又可以令啲人唔會唔敢答/問問題<br />\n咩都全級一齊上，可以聽埋啲勁人問問題<br />\n啲問題真係問得好好，professor 又可以教多啲大家又學多啲<br />\n重點係，可以成日見返PW 醫生，好似有得出多次PW med 同PW surg！！！好幸福！！！&quot;"},{"pid":"89618ca7199e826596182181b586e1ac0abdf522","tid":1887430,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"老老實實我覺得大學依一年要加學費"},{"pid":"3ed08b6afb03daff5e8765a6166d7ea9ff04f8d3","tid":1887430,"uid":146917,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"樓豬係毒撚"},{"pid":"17926c2421f0931579a21f8435fdf3885717da10","tid":1887430,"uid":79562,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"識人錄底女同學視訊再丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db97344773d88b320a1f6343769519ef28d21a31","tid":1887430,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17926c2421f0931579a21f8435fdf3885717da10","tid":1887430,"uid":79562,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"識人錄底女同學視訊再丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T14:05:30.000Z","msg":"Me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db3bb1645ac3828d2b8b56c4ef517a510b831c6","tid":1887430,"uid":241543,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"17926c2421f0